Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.38,0:00:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know there's an awesome\Ntreasure at the end of this sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whoever gets it can be King\Nof the Pirates! Isn't that exciting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unheard-of adventures are waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage! Let that shred of courage grow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The horizons everyone\Ndreamed of were separate at first
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:01:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now they can be seen\Nthrough a single telescope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.82,0:01:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bitter compass of destiny\Nis leading your heart astray
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so turn the wheel in the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toss aside your bonds and your past
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can surely smile despite that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears shed trying to achieve\Nyour dreams aren't for naught
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Precious in my life
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught a glimpse of\Nthe tail end to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:02:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Going Merry fell right into the\Nmiddle of a Naval base, Navarone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.45,0:02:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and the others dispersed\Nunder the cover of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami successfully disguised\Nherself as a cleaning person.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"On Duty"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.13,0:02:18.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Sanji slipped into\Nthe dining hall as cooks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, one of the crew,\NZoro, has been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Navarone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.51,0:02:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captured Zoro and\NChopper's Emergency Operations!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So six more, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the Straw Hat Pirates, Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drake, shall we try questioning him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.87,0:02:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you told us to check\Nthe dining hall, Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.47,0:03:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that everyone gets hungry,\Nso they're likely to appear in the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the dining hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jessica told me that new cooks from\Nheadquarters are coming as well, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.52,0:03:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should we proceed\Nwith questioning Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:18.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Justice"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.54,0:03:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... What the hell's with these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.26,0:03:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I'll take it easy for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir, Lt. Commander Drake!\NBut he's extremely dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By order of Vice Admiral Jonathan,\NI'll question Roronoa Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.21,0:04:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro... You used\Nto be called a pirate hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.25,0:04:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would never have imagined that you'd\Nbe a member of the Straw Hat Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you came all the\Nway here to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you come from?!\NHow many of you are there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.93,0:04:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your purpose\Nin invading this fortress?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a good strategy to invade this\N"hedgehog" fortress from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you do it?\NDid you build a launch pad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.61,0:04:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we came from heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mocking you or anything.\NWe really came from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't intend to go along with such a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said, we came from heaven\Nby riding a floating octopus balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.32,0:05:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.59,0:05:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you insist on that, no matter what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.26,0:05:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make light of the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.60,0:05:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you tell\Nus the truth at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:24.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"On Duty"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.99,0:05:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, you'll be in charge of\Ncleaning this exercise hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.99,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"On Duty"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to clean this... by myself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give the floor a good polish!\NYou'll enjoy lunch after your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This disguise may have been a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that one of the\NStraw Hat Pirates was captured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That wasn't a ghost ship, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.00,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, in a sense, it's scarier than ghosts.\NDon't be surprised when I tell you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.00,0:06:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Roronoa Zoro, the pirate hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be other\Ncrewmembers hiding, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.34,0:06:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could find even one\Nof them, we'd get noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.34,0:06:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that Zoro was caught...!\NWhat am I gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.39,0:06:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to what they just said,\Neveryone else seems to be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:42.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I wanna get out of here already!\NBut I don't know where they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't know what to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I continue to live like this,\NI'll break down before I get caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.38,0:07:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have to come up with\Na different disguise... Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.39,0:07:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This isn't good! It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.06,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The raccoon dog went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.73,0:07:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! The corner is raccoon dogged...\Nno, the raccoon dog is cornered!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.73,0:07:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?! What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he really was a raccoon dog.\NHe disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.12,0:07:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a lot of work finding him in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ah!\N--Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.74,0:08:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.45,0:08:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're these?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he leave just his antlers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? But with just antlers,\Nwe can't even make a pot dish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Did we lose him on our way here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.30,0:08:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the package?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.47,0:08:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.81,0:08:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing with deer antlers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.14,0:08:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that they'll be used\Nas ingredients for medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.18,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that they ran into a storm.\NMany were injured. Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.19,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take them to the medical room quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see... Plunge the scalpel\Nvertically, and if it bleeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.64,0:09:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood, blood, blood...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.86,0:09:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly! Why did all the doctors\Nhave to go on a business trip at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.20,0:09:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God, please don't\Nsend any surgery patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Medical Room Chief!\N--Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We brought the deer antlers,\Nthe medicine ingredient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Please leave them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.26,0:10:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I look pretty good in this uniform,\Nif I do say so myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine if I look like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you apologizing for?!\NGo to the medical room already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Hm? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an emergency!\NAll the nurses are being called in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it... I'm screwed no\Nmatter what clothes I wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kobato! It's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.95,0:10:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Internal case? Pediatrics? Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're quite a few seriously\Ninjured marines on the Stan Marey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Surgery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.55,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll leave them to you nurses,\Nsince surgery isn't my field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying?! You're the\Nonly doctor in this base right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.33,0:10:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...! I'm a pediatrician and,\Num, surgery is outside my field!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... This seems to be a medical room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.01,0:10:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder if that doctor is gonna be okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy! Did they run\Ninto a cyclone or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.01,0:11:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, treat their injuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! I don't have time for stuff like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to quickly find the Going Merry\Nand leave this place right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop daydreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.39,0:11:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, what should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.86,0:11:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right... right... Give him 50 mg of painkiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.50,0:11:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about preparing the operation room?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.07,0:11:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Operation?! Operation...\NYeah, he needs an operation...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doctor! There's no time to lose!\N--Please get a grip!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please advise us on treating the patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.05,0:12:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Doctor...\N--I can't just stand back and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll advise you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, give this patient phenicol,\Ncardiotonic and tialcillin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.07,0:12:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Respond if you got that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.08,0:12:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perform cross-matching\Nwith each patient's blood type!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who require an operation,\Ngive them preoperative treatment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that patient a tetanus\Ntoxoid and 5 mg of morphine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.12,0:12:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the operation room ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring the patients in,\Nstarting with seriously injured ones!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.46,0:12:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.57,0:13:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a grip, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami! What are you doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me... I don't know\Nwhat's going on, since I fainted...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.62,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... a doctor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who you are, but you\Nsaved us with your apt instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're not saved yet!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're a number of soldiers whose lives\Nare in danger without an operation!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the operations on seriously\Ninjured patients as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.14,0:13:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Operations...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.52,0:13:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear things like seeing\Npeople in pain and bleeding at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I'm really terrible even at giving shots,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.86,0:14:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to think of cutting a human body\Nor putting stitches on it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this! This is a naval base, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been giving treatments\Nuntil now if you're like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.47,0:14:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My field is pediatrics. Since the other\Ndoctors are all out on business trips,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.15,0:14:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was asked to serve as a\Ndeputy Medical Room Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deputy or not, you're the\NMedical Room Chief right now, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, more or less...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More or less?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Let's get out of here already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get out! This place isn't\Na lake! It's connected to the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get out with the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I can't go yet.\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.00,0:14:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a doctor, a person that\Nsaves people's lives, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... but even for a doctor,\Nthere're things they can and can't do...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.88,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person who taught me\Nmedicine told me this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:15:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a man who was told by\Nhis doctor that he was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.86,0:15:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wandered in despair,\Nsearching for a place to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as he was passing over a mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he saw vivid cherry blossoms\Nblooming all over the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.21,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to see a doctor again.\NAnd the doctor said to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're completely healthy."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only doctor to the patients here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.05,0:15:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't give up! There's no illness\Nin this world that can't be healed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't say that\Nthere're things you can't do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.26,0:15:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're no patients that\Nwe doctors can't heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctors can make miracles happen!\NAt least, we have to believe that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.44,0:15:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will I be able to see\Nthe cherry blossoms, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.48,0:16:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather... can I show the cherry\Nblossoms to people who're suffering?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course! I'll help you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! We don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't, but people's lives have\Npriority over anything! I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?! You'll get left behind,\Nyou know! Is that what you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, preparations for\Nthe operations are ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.31,0:16:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'll be right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chop... Dr. Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.32,0:16:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.50,0:16:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to leave me behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I leave here now,\NI'll be scolded by Doctorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.17,0:16:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you know we can't\Njust leave without you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:02.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"Operating Room"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a doctor like that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll start the emergency operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.17,0:17:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a piece of iron in his chest.\NWe need to remove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The patient is already sleeping\Nsoundly from the anesthesia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.85,0:17:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Scalpel!\N--Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.72,0:17:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kobato! You'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who can show\Ncherry blossoms to this patient!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.23,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's near an artery, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.90,0:18:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, suction!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.34,0:18:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The iron piece has been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I did it!\N--This is no time to celebrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There're many other patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.06,0:18:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes!\N--Let's give it our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.90,0:18:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A doctor you've never\Nseen is performing an operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.24,0:18:36.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be one of the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:38.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.58,0:18:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of\Nan operation. Please leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.58,0:18:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an emergency! Dr. Kobato,\NI wanna ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Kobato! His blood pressure is dropping!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.29,0:18:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give him 6 units of red blood cell\Nsuspension and 1 unit of platelets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.23,0:19:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.30,0:19:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. Continue the blood\Ntransfusion! Also have dopamine ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.07,0:19:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dr. Kobato!\N--We're in the middle of an\Nemergency operation! Please be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're operating?! You fainted when\Nyou saw blood flowing out of my arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor we've never seen\Nbefore should be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.62,0:19:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're interrupting!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.29,0:19:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you'll find in here are doctors and nurses\Ngiving their all to save precious lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Monitor them.\N--Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suture completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, that was the last patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, Dr. Kobato!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.37,0:20:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a great doctor, Dr. Kobato.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all... but you are a\Ngreat doctor, Mr. Raccoon Dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.85,0:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy! I'm not a\Nraccoon dog! I'm a reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't she be rather surprised\Nto see Chopper like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, what am I doing in a place like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know if Nami-san\Nand Robin-chan are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! But out of regard for Jessica-san,\NI can't just abandon this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.44,0:20:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.11,0:20:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.11,0:20:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was watching this thing\Nand admiring how incredible it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.28,0:21:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either help me out or come up\Nwith a way to get us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I wonder why we're not\Ngetting out of this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's come to this because you were dawdling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.09,0:21:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Say, Sanji...\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.10,0:21:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Octopuses can be eaten raw, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.10,0:21:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it? Is your stuff ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.94,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take your time, the next\N100 soldiers are gonna show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jessica-san! I've just finished it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?! It's finally break time? I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.61,0:21:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd like you to chop up 300 more onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is she a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! I'm your servant, Jessica-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.16,0:21:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! It's your fault it's come to this, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.31,0:22:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get moving towards the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.65,0:22:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's move ahead, pursuing our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the answers are right here, pouring out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.51,0:22:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rush forth, rush forth,\Non the road opened before us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep moving forward! We can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.25,0:22:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't give in, we won't give in,\Neven if the obstacle is big
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing to be scared of,\Nwe can overcome it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That bastard! That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.18,0:23:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, are the others okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.49,0:23:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Usopp! Is our ship all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin, why're you dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.72,0:23:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain and the idiot cook...\NNever mind about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.89,0:23:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the situation is starting to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.89,0:23:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--On the next episode of One Piece!\N--Don't read my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Navy's Dragnet Closes In!\NThe Second Member Captured!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be a great swordsman!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.24,0:23:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.74,0:23:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
